{
  "stem": "24409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everyone was arrested who was on the boat, but I have pictures.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were behind barbed wire, but they were happy they were at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After a few months, they were released.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was soon followed by another ship, the [INAUDIBLE], and the ship which had traveled with the British, too, and it broke through, too and beached itself on the-- on the beach farther-- farther south or north-- farther north.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 17,000 to 18,000 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were in our ships.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all together about 40,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have the statistics in my-- in my book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British figured-- the British had registered 20,100 and some immigrants between the fall of 1939 and the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But first of all, we started it long before 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the fall of 1939, with several thousand in already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they didn't get everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't know of everybody, because besides us, there were steamer parties of 10 and 12 who left the Yugoslav port or Bulgarian ports, that's the family [INAUDIBLE] and made it there because they knew about it, that you can do it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I estimate that the figure of 20,100 or so of the British can easily be doubled because they started counting late and they have, by far, not all the people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I think I have to end now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you feel like we need to stop let's stop it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm too shaky now.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
